ose associates. </p>		\n			<figure><img src=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" /></figure><h3>Fatima</h3><p>She has a background in marketing and finance and is placed as the strategic head of the company. Her strength is goal-management and is considered to be a great task-master. She is focused and driven towards achieving results. She brings her reflective nature into making sound marketing strategies by evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of your on-going program. She is often the one who creates process steps with her engineered approach and solves problems with a long-term perspective. </p>","About","","inherit","closed","closed","","13-revision-v1","","","2019-01-09 07:51:48","2019-01-09 07:51:48","",13,"http://consulting-site.local/blog/13-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
