300px\" /></figure><h3>Fatima</h3><p>She has a background in marketing and finance and is placed as the strategic head of the company. Her strength is goal-management and is considered to be a great task-master. She is focused and driven towards achieving results. She brings her reflective nature into making sound marketing strategies by evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of your on-going program. She is often the one who creates process steps with her engineered approach and solves problems with a long-term perspective. </p>		\n			<h2>Services</h2>		\n		<p>Ima Solution focuses on using data within every aspect of business decision making. All of our services are data-driven and oriented in a manner that generates more meaningful data for you. Here are the types of consultation that you can opt for:</p>		\n									<a href=\"\">Strategic planning and management</a>\n									<a href=\"\">Business shrink</a>\n									<a href=\"\">Ops Consultation</a>\n									<a href=\"\">IT Consultation </a>\n									<a href=\"\">Marketing Consultation </a>\n									<a href=\"\">Content strategy</a>\n									Strategic planning and management\n					<p>Want to chart out a plan ahead? Then it is essential to building in a strategic plan based on research and market knowledge. Strategic planning consultation includes:</p><ul><li>Business plan</li><li>Execution directives</li><li>Market research</li><li>Risk analysis</li><li>Competition analysis</li><li>Expert recommendations</li><li>Price quotes</li><li>Documentation and process steps</li><li>Business set up</li></ul><p>Knowing that you are making an informed decision is by itself a great relief and then add to it the benefits of making good choices. Get in touch with the Ima experts today.</p>\n									Business shrink\n					<p>Our business shrinks are here to listen to your business issues and offer researched recommendations. Ima Solution provides:</p><ul><li>Problem analysis</li><li>Business health check-up</li><li>Quality control</li><li>Business personnel management</li><li>Customized solutions</li><li>Data capture points</li><li>Data analysis</li><li>Implementing management theories into practice</li></ul><p>A problem addressed at the right time could make all the difference to the survival and growth of a company. Get a business shrink for your problems today.</p>\n									Ops Consultation\n					<p>This is often the responsible factor for poor performance even though a great plan was charted. Ima Solution helps with building processes through:</p><ul><li>Tracking current process performance</li><li>Mapping process steps</li><li>Cost-benefit analysis</li><li>Re-engineering processes</li></ul><p>Base it on your existing data to maintain the quality of work. You can use an ops consultation to reduce downtime, defects, and the number of steps required to complete a job. Get one for your business today.</p>\n									IT Consultation \n					<p>This is the age of IT developments and every business has either moved to online operations, is moving currently or directly starts on Cloud. Ima Solution can help you:</p><ul><li>Build customized products</li><li>Use existing data in a way that is meaningful for the business</li><li>Integrate systems to form a manageable and cohesive workspace</li><li>Keep the focus on internal and external customers</li></ul><p>Manage operation, maintain and track data to work in a world of enhanced capabilities and meet the ever-changing needs of running a business. An IT consultation is the key to your business growth. Get it right away.</p>\n									Marketing Consultation \n					<p>A marketing consultation for your business segment can help you understand what is working for your business. You can also find out if what you spend on marketing activities is getting utilized effectively. The Ima consultant provides:</p><ul><li>Branding</li><li>Market positioning</li><li>Digital media strategy</li><li>Marketing health check-up and evaluation of current marketing campaigns</li><li>Marketing Roadmap</li></ul><p>A confident marketing strategy is what keeps your business on track, so double checking that it is effective is appropriate. Contact Ima Solution for your marketing problems right away.</p>\n									Content strategy\n					<p>Your business depends upon the content that you share with your internal and external stakeholders. Ima Solution helps you:</p><ul><li>Build a content strategy for your company</li><li>Create a content roadmap for the next year</li><li>Create content for website, brochures, email marketing, presentations, PR posts, SEO pages, white papers and much more</li><li>Edit and proofread existing content</li></ul><p>Content is king and talking about what your audiences want to know is most beneficial for your business. Get the Ima experts to create a content strategy for you now.</p>","Home","","inherit","closed","closed","","12-revision-v1","","","2019-01-09 08:55:08","2019-01-09 08:55:08","",12,"http://consulting-site.local/blog/12-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
