(242,1,"2019-01-10 00:32:48","2019-01-10 00:32:48","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At Ima Solution, we recognize that business organizations\nrun on people making effective decisions. Managers may indeed be capable of a\nlot but “everything” might just be excessive. Often in this pursuit, they end\nup taking major chunks of work, juggling between activities at almost all\ntimes. While it might look like a lot of work is getting done, it is the\nquality of work that suffers. Not to mention those few burdened souls. This\nkind of over-working impacts a business leader on two fronts, personal and\nprofessional. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At the professional front, decision making and operations\nare affected. A strategic vision is lost and even small business problems are\namplified. A business consultation service touches even the personal aspect of\nthis problem by making a lasting impact on running your business better. Ima\nSolution offers business consultation services in order to get you back on\ntrack and focus on the things that matter. The consultation is wholesome and\nbased on data so that the path forward caters to specific individual\nrequirements. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A business consultant can help you manage change, optimize\nprocesses, learn about best practices, glide through a tough period, and infuse\na fresh and creative take on your business. Ima Solution’s strong emphasis on\ndata helps with evaluating the long-term impact of crucial business decisions.\nChart a healthy way forward for yourself and get in touch with the Ima team\ntoday! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","How can a business consultation help you?","","inherit","closed","closed","","1-revision-v1","","","2019-01-10 00:32:48","2019-01-10 00:32:48","",1,"http://consulting-site.local/blog/1-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
