(263,1,"2019-01-10 01:06:11","2019-01-10 01:06:11","<p>Ima Solution was founded in 2014 with a strong recognition of the fact that business issues need to be addressed in a systematized format. With extensive market research and experience of business-related problems, we found that:</p><ul><li>Taking responsibility for decision-making is a key pain area for a majority of running businesses where some managers are constantly second-guessing their decisions</li><li>Data is either not getting captured or utilized to its full potential</li><li>Processes aren’t well-defined, documented and optimized</li><li>Risks are not covered within the decision-making process making the business more prone to market threats</li><li>Systems, technology, and communication channels are not in-line with business requirements</li></ul><p>Ima Solution was started as a journey to try and mitigate these pain-points. We help business leaders, managers and entrepreneurs make decisions confidently, backed by data and ingrained with real experience.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/person1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/person1.png 300w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/person1-150x150.png 150w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/person1-230x230.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></figure><h3>Moiz</h3><p>A young, dynamic and quality leader who has an unreal fascination with numbers and data. He sees patterns in data and his love affair with data trends and analysis is long-standing. He is a business consultant with over 11 years of experience working with many Fortune 500 companies. Risk analysis, inclination to implement and improve the IT structure in organizations and customer-centricity make him a wholesome consultant. He started the business shrink phenomena and is known as a data whisperer by his c