(331,1,"2019-01-10 06:06:29","2019-01-10 06:06:29","<p>Ima Solution was founded in 2014 with a strong recognition of the fact that business issues need to be addressed in a systematized format. With extensive market research and experience of business-related problems, we found that:</p><ul><li>Taking responsibility for decision-making is a key pain area for a majority of running businesses where some managers are constantly second-guessing their decisions</li><li>Data is either not getting captured or utilized to its full potential</li><li>Processes aren’t well-defined, documented and optimized</li><li>Risks are not covered within the decision-making process making the business more prone to market threats</li><li>Systems, technology, and communication channels are not in-line with business requirements</li></ul><p>Ima Solution was started as a journey to try and mitigate these pain-points. We help business leaders, managers and entrepreneurs make decisions confidently, backed by data and ingrained with real experience.</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3.jpg 400w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3-150x150.jpg 150w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3-300x300.jpg 300w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3-230x230.jpg 230w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/3-350x350.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></figure><h3>Moiz</h3><p>A young, dynamic and quality leader who has an unreal fascination with numbers and data. He sees patterns in data and his love affair with data trends and analysis is long-standing. He is a business consultant with over 11 years of experience working with many Fortune 500 companies. Risk analysis, inclination to implement and improve the IT structure in organizations and customer-centricity make him a wholesome consultant. He started the business shrink phenomena and is known as a data whisperer by his close associates. ​</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6.jpg 400w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6-150x150.jpg 150w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6-300x300.jpg 300w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6-230x230.jpg 230w, http://consulting-site.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/emp6-350x350.jpg 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></figure><h3>Fatima</h3><p>She has a background in marketing and finance and is placed as the strategic head of the company. Her strength is goal-management and is considered to be a great task-master. She is focused and driven towards achieving results. She brings her reflective nature into making sound marketing strategies by evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of your on-going program. She is often the one who creates process steps with her engineered approach and solves problems with a long-term perspective.</p>","About","","inherit","closed","closed","","13-revision-v1","","","2019-01-10 06:06:29","2019-01-10 06:06:29","",13,"http://consulting-site.local/blog/13-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
